-04-22T10:11:57.000Z","msg":"笑下算<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.compcomm.hk/tc/media/press/files/Auto_fuel_Market_Study_Report_ExSummary_Chi.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.compcomm.hk%2Ftc%2Fmedia%2Fpress%2Ffiles%2FAuto_fuel_Market_Study_Report_ExSummary_Chi.pdf&d=ltyh5TmdzGcNJFTF%2BAmR8oVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=5f76faf1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.compcomm.hk/tc/media/press/files/Auto_fuel_Market_Study_Report_ExSummary_Chi.pdf</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T22:26:57.000Z","msg":"擺明政府收左錢扮睇唔到<br />\n間間次次一樣價咁都叫無合謀搵鬼信<br />\n所以必須光復香港 真普選"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T03:10:46.000Z","msg":"你諗下<br />\n而家減埋2.5其實係14蚊<br />\n政府抽稅$6.06/L佔4成幾<br />\n<br />\n仲有<br />\n地政總署今日（四月十六日）公布三幅加油站用地的招標結果。三幅用地的批租期為二十一年，地價總計為十三億六千五百二十六萬零八百八十四元。<br />\n平均每個站每年2200萬，一個站汽油柴油石油氣加埋一年都係得千幾萬公升，平均每L油又收多個幾兩蚊地價，fatfat<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲未計利得稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果油平，油公司投地自然唔出咁高價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果油公司利潤低，利得稅自然少咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係如果你係油公司老闆，老細你會唔會由得個政府袋得多過你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n與其大家蝕，不如大家賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8195b85e0f1e931887f4282e15dd71405ecdcc6","tid":1983150,"uid":26168,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"79607f778ae710f80ab28aa282aef3dcb178eccc","tid":1983150,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e211684d2b5eee5082a6618e1a31cb633dfb8bd3","tid":1983150,"uid":18074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T08:34:03.000Z","msg":"呢兩日都無減過價喎，咩玩法"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T10:04:57.000Z","msg":"話左高位個時買入...."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T15:52:34.000Z","msg":"油價升佢地即加架喎，唔會話低位嗰時買入咗架喎"},{"pid":"0c9ee2ab45b5f784bfc4d743ebfde72c01c1